text: Dillingen (district) () is a rural district in Swabia in southwest Bavaria, Germany. Neighbor districts are: Donau-Ries, Augsburg (district), Günzburg (district) and in Baden-Württemberg: Heidenheim (district); Dillingen is the capital of Dillingen (district). ==Towns and municipalities== Towns Municipalities #Dillingen an der Donau #Gundelfingen an der Donau #Höchstädt an der Donau #Lauingen #Wertingen #Aislingen #Bachhagel #Bächingen #Binswangen #Bissingen #Blindheim #Buttenwiesen #Finningen #Glött #Haunsheim #Holzheim 12.
